{
  "stem": "2830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there was no-- he didn't--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't know that you're not supposed to be in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're all standing up for a nice Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, and then when we sat down, everybody else sat down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we had something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I still-- no matter what you're going to do, it was always on my mind, I'm going to be caught any minute.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just-- there was a time that I can really enjoy it, being in a place like this, and see those Nazis.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I really didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just saw, dear God, am I-- am I for real?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it that I'm here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then when we walked out, we were finished, they stood up again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Heil Hitler again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can laugh at it now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on our way to that school, where we came to a park.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was already with-- with our teacher, brought him out, that kid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "About eight years old already, wearing, you know, those knee socks and the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uniform and everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a short discussion, and he looked at the clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to be in time, you know, to get back, because it takes so many hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was already 8:00 in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By 10 o'clock, the gates get closed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No-- you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't get in anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't get in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he figured out for me to-- to be in time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] He didn't worry about himself, because he didn't live there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We arrived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was after 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took-- the train was so late, or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we got out from the train, the sky lit up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was an air raid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The whole sky was a piece of fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
